{"questionId":"358f18bc","correctAnswer":"1728","section":"Math","steps":[{"title":"Find the vertex x-coordinate","content":"$f(x)=x^2-48x+2304$, so $a=1$, $b=-48$.<br/>$$x=-\\frac{b}{2a}=-\\frac{-48}{2(1)}=24$$"},{"title":"Evaluate $f(24)$ to get the minimum","content":"$$f(24)=24^2-48(24)+2304=576-1152+2304=\\mathbf{1728}$$<br/>The answer is <strong>1728</strong>.","desmosExpressions":["f(x)=x^2-48x+2304","(24,1728)"]}]}